Author: riiiiising
Title: [ANN][ICO]TradeBit - First mobile solutions for managing your cryptocurrencies!
Body: That is not true for most parts in the world. In almost every country paying with crypto is a taxable event (capital gains). And changing BTC into ETH is also a taxable event almost anywhere in the world. You should get familiar with that stuff before you build blockchain solutions

Author: l4s7re4lg4mer
Title: [ANN][ICO]TradeBit - First mobile solutions for managing your cryptocurrencies!
Body: I think you didn't catch the whole idea of the project.  We are building a platform for managing your cryptocurrencies.  1. Automated Portfolio tracking 2. Trading Signals and Portfolio insights 3. Coaching System 4. Trading via API 5. Exchange with top 200 support 6. Ranking system for cryptocurrencies 7. Universal wallet 8. 3rd party add-ons 9. One click FIAT /Crypto/Fiat conversion  So the feature "9" is where we want to allow our user's possibility to spend their cryptocurrencies directly from our wallet or exchange without any taxes coming from us. Now you have to use a lot of 3rd party software to get that done and you pay a lot of extra taxes. As I said before we are not going to avoid legal authorities taxes in any way, but we want to release our users from the extra taxation and fees they pay to third party companies for nothing.  Thanks

Title: [ANN][ICO]TradeBit - First mobile solutions for managing your cryptocurrencies!
Body: An Open Letter to the Community from TradeBit’s team  We are happy to announce that we significantly increase the rate for investors: from 7500 to 120000 in Phase 1 from 6250 to 100000 in Phase 2 from 5000 to 80000 in Phase 3 Which is 16 times more. The supply stays the same - 500 000 000 TBT. For the bounty campaign, we will release our emergency supply which 10 000 000 TBT and the 5 000 000 TBT from the marketing supply. In total 20 000 000 TBT (4% of the whole supply).  The ETH address is already changed. For all the investors already purchased at the previous rates will be compensated immediately after the new rates are applied! Bounty subscribers will also transition to the new rates accordingly.  By giving this opportunity to the investors we are going to reduce the HARD CAP of the crowdsale from 50000 ETH to 3000 ETH.  We want to thank each and every one of you for being a part of our community.  Best regards, TradeBit Team.

Title: [ANN][ICO]TradeBit - First mobile solutions for managing your cryptocurrencies!
Body: Well, many financial specialists expect the price of the bitcoin to rise to 100 000$ by the end of the year, which will make cryptocurrencies even more famous than now. If that happens market cap will rise tremendously and with it, all altcoins will rise also. So that makes TBT tokens at the moment, one of the best investment opportunities with very low risk as by investing even just 100$, they can turn into 10 000$ just for one year and what makes it even better is that we already have the first version of our product released and working wheres, there are other cryptocurrencies which have a lot bigger price and no product nor nothing to back it up.  So to sum the things up by taking into account the price for 1TBT is 0.008$ which is less than 1 cent this will put the project to an average market cap of 4 000 000$ which will rank us somewhere at the place of 600th in cryptocurrency ranking table. So even by just entering top 200 cryptocurrencies, you will have 25x ROI and, if we enter top 50 which is our target for 2018 you will have 150x ROI. So that will turn your 100$ to 15 000$ in no time.

Author: l4s7re4lg4mer
Title: [ANN][ICO]TradeBit - First mobile solutions for managing your cryptocurrencies!
Body: Website | Facebook | Twitter | Telegram | LinkedIn   https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/High-Res.jpg  WHO ARE WE:   TradeBit was formed by a team of young and devoted enthusiast who are eager leave their mark in the ever-expanding world of technology. We share the vision of the blockchain technology originally developed by Satoshi Nakamoto. We want to expand his vision. We want to remove the centralized banking system which only steals from people and form of fees and taxes. However, with the birth of blockchain technology, many fake cryptocurrencies popped out saying that they will be next bitcoin. We don’t want our token to be next BitCoin, we want our token to allow people to reach to bitcoin and other valuable cryptocurrencies easier without the hassle of paying enormous taxes and fees.  Our team consists of Cryptocurrency enthusiast which share a common vision for the future, so we decided to make the change and develop something new and valuable.  https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Team.png  INTRODUCTION:   TradeBit will be first cryptocurrency platform, that combines automated portfolio tracking, cryptocurrencies signals, investment insight, trading support for all the current exchanges API. Later in the roadmap, you can see we will develop our own exchanges, which will be the first one to support all the top 200 cryptocurrencies at the same time. We are also developing coaching system as well, so users with more experience can share it with newcomers and make a profit in TBT token.  UPDATE  An Open Letter to the Community from TradeBit’s team  We are happy to announce that we significantly increase the rate for investors: from 7500 to 120000 in Phase 1 from 6250 to 100000 in Phase 2 from 5000 to 80000 in Phase 3 Which is 16 times more. The supply stays the same - 500 000 000 TBT. For the bounty campaign, we will release our emergency supply which 10 000 000 TBT and the 5 000 000 TBT from the marketing supply. In total 20 000 000 TBT (4% of the whole supply).  The ETH address is already changed. For all the investors already purchased on the previous rates will be compensated immediately after the new rates are applied! Bounty subscribers will also transition to the new rates accordingly.  By giving this opportunity to the investors we are going to reduce the HARD CAP of the crowdsale from 50000 ETH to 3000 ETH.  We want to thank each and every one of you for being a part of our community.  Best regards, TradeBit Team.  https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/token-slae.png TRADEBIT PLATFORM:   https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/TradeBit_LandingPage_11-1.pnghttps://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/TradeBit_LandingPage_13.png   Exchange with support for all top 200 cryptocurrencies at the same time. https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/TradeBit_LandingPage_34.png   TOKEN USAGE:  TradeBit Token will be used as a payment method inside our platform. In order to access all the cool features, you will have to use your token inside. Also, they will be used as a payment method from user to user for sharing trading signals and investment insight. If you want to teach and get into the cryptocurrency world faster, you will have the possibility to learn from the best.  MVP:   https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/TradeBit_LandingPage_15.png Android App | IOS - cooming soon  https://www.tradebit.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/roadmap.png  BOUNTY:   For our bounty program please visit bounty thread.
